OL,3,CExtension to Borders Railway set to
OL,4,Cprogress to next phase
OL,6,FThe campaign to extend the Borders
OL,7,FRailway beyond Tweedbank and down to
OL,8,FCarlisle is set to progress to the
OL,9,Fnext phase.
OL,11,FThe Department for Transport
OL,12,Fpreviously announced #10m in funding
OL,13,Fcommitted by the UK and Scottish
OL,14,FGovernments through the Borderlands
OL,15,FInclusive Growth Deal.
OL,17,FThe next stage will see a project
OL,18,Fmanager appointed to lead the business
OL,19,Fcase for the project.
