OL,3,CExtension to Borders Railway set to
OL,4,Cprogress to next phase
OL,6,FUK Government Scotland Office Minister
OL,7,FKirsty McNeill said: "Growth is a
OL,8,Fpriority mission for the UK Government
OL,9,Fand we've been clear that the #450
OL,10,Fmillion Borderlands Inclusive Growth
OL,11,FDeal spanning southern Scotland and
OL,12,Fnorthern England is vital to achieving
OL,13,Fthis.
OL,15,F"It's great news that the UK
OL,16,FDepartment for Transport has now
OL,17,Fconfirmed up to #5 million towards
OL,18,Ffeasibility work to explore the
OL,19,Fpotential to extend the Borders
OL,20,FRailway from Tweedbank to Carlisle.
