OL,3,CExtension to Borders Railway set to
OL,4,Cprogress to next phase
OL,6,F"We look forward to working with deal
OL,7,Fpartners as the feasibility work
OL,8,Fprogresses.
OL,10,F"The UK Government is focused on
OL,11,Fdelivering our Plan for Change to
OL,12,Fturbo-charge economic growth and
OL,13,Fdeliver a decade of national renewal
OL,14,Fand opportunity for all.
OL,16,F"This includes investing nearly #1.4
OL,17,Fbillion into important local projects
OL,18,Facross Scotland over the next ten
OL,19,Fyears, including the Borders."
