OL,3,CExtension to Borders Railway set to
OL,4,Cprogress to next phase
OL,6,FExtending the railway could see trains
OL,7,Ftravel through towns such as Hawick
OL,8,Fwhich would improve connectivity in
OL,9,Fthe Borders for tourists and residents.
OL,11,FCabinet Secretary for Transport Fiona
OL,12,FHyslop said: "The Scottish Government
OL,13,Fbelieves in strong investment in
OL,14,Fpublic transport and looks forward to
OL,15,Fthe 10th anniversary of the Borders
OL,16,FRailway later this year, which will be
OL,17,Fa celebration of the transformation it
OL,18,Fhas delivered to this region.
