OL,3,CExtension to Borders Railway set to
OL,4,Cprogress to next phase
OL,6,F"We remain committed to providing up
OL,7,Fto #5 million for this business
OL,8,Fcasework as part of our #65 million
OL,9,Finvestment in the region through the
OL,10,FBorderlands deal.
OL,12,F"We welcome the news that the UK
OL,13,FGovernment will now match our
OL,14,Fcommitment of up to #5 million for a
OL,15,Ffeasibility study to extend the
OL,16,FBorders Railway and are supportive of
OL,17,Fpartners securing a project manager
OL,18,Fwith the technical expertise to
OL,19,Fdeliver the project well."
