OL,3,CExtension to Borders Railway set to
OL,4,Cprogress to next phase
OL,6,FThe Borderlands Inclusive Growth Deal
OL,7,Fwas signed in 2021 and has supported
OL,8,Fover #450 million worth of projects.
OL,10,FCouncillor Euan Jardine, Leader of
OL,11,FScottish Borders Council, said:
OL,12,F"Thanks to the unwavering support of
OL,13,Fthe Borderlands Partnership and their
OL,14,Ftireless campaign, as well as the
OL,15,Fcrucial funding and commitment from
OL,16,Fboth the Scottish Government and the
OL,17,FUK Government, we are making
OL,18,Fsignificant strides towards the
OL,19,FBorders Railway extension.
